# Metagenomic analysis scripts

This repository contains scripts used for downstream analysis and figure generation
in the manuscript:

"Gut Microbiota Dysbiosis and Immune Correlations in Pediatric Mycoplasma Pneumoniae Pneumonia"

## Contents
- alpha_diversity.R: Alpha diversity analysis (Chao1, Shannon)
- beta_diversity.R: Beta diversity analysis (Brayâ€“Curtis, PCoA)
- lefse_prepare.R: Preparation of input files for LEfSe
- correlation_heatmap.R: Spearman correlation analysis and heatmap visualization
- stats_basic.R: Statistical testing and data preprocessing

## Notes
- Raw metagenomic sequencing data are deposited in NCBI SRA.
- Scripts are provided for reproducibility of analyses reported in the Results section.
